        "bug_type": "代码段未加载(DataAbort)",
        "symptoms": [
          "DataAbort",
          "FotaTrig死机",
          "BIST残留",
          "PSRAM未加载"
        ],
        "root_cause": "`NON_OTA_CODE_IN_PSRAM` 段未从Flash搬运到PSRAM，CPU执行BIST内存测试残留数据(0xAA/0x55)触发Permission fault，FAULT_ADDRESS=0x4",
        "call_chain_summary": "`fota_trigger_worker_thread()` (PL_CODE_IN_PSRAM,已加载) → `nwy_fota_get_reboot_count()` (NON_OTA_CODE_IN_PSRAM,未加载) → BIST残留 → DataAbort",
        "keywords": [
          "DataAbort",
